{"tid":888902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★新治癒！蘭州----高速貨車失控連撞31車　釀至少11死31傷","createTime":"2018-11-04T07:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T07:54:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ca2fba221fca7b427470cd03b93bded437df048a","tid":888902,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T07:05:13.000Z","msg":"據央視新聞今天（3日）消息，今晚7點21分，G75蘭海高速（蘭州到海口）蘭州南收費站發生交通事故，一輛貨車失控從收費站衝下連撞31輛車。<br />\n<br />\n初步了解，事故造成31人受傷，11人重傷，11人死亡。交警及救援人員趕到現場，截至目前車內被困人員已全部救出。蘭州南收費廣場雙向臨時管制。<br />\n<br />\n從網民發布的視頻可見，現場被撞車輛損毀嚴重，部件散落一地。還傳出女子呼救聲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/254829/慘重車禍-有片-蘭海高速貨車失控連撞31車-釀至少11死31傷\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F254829%2F%E6%85%98%E9%87%8D%E8%BB%8A%E7%A6%8D-%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-%E8%98%AD%E6%B5%B7%E9%AB%98%E9%80%9F%E8%B2%A8%E8%BB%8A%E5%A4%B1%E6%8E%A7%E9%80%A3%E6%92%9E31%E8%BB%8A-%E9%87%80%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%9111%E6%AD%BB31%E5%82%B7&d=8dA%2FicDEPNKOZgrjHyrZlkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=58ee61bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/254829/慘重車禍-有片-蘭海高速貨車失控連撞31車-釀至少11死31傷</a>"},{"pid":"a889c3b777e139855fe704ec60f846ab0f82cce1","tid":888902,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T07:06:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oXwS2RG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoXwS2RG.png&h=0397405a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"94e681a20e73d21434c2e0198b9df9be2864011c","tid":888902,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T07:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.